'Tell me about yourself...'

What I value: Kindness, Innovation, Integrity, Stoicism
What I want: Success, Balance, Happiness
What I hope for: A clinical research practive with flexibility. Split 60/40 between clinic and research hours. 
  Treating patients, researching cures. Having balance in life to spend it with my loved ones.
What do I want others to see: My kindness, my intelligence, my ambition
What do I want to leave: The world better than I inherited it. Lives I touch improved by my words and actions

Summary: To live a balanced life on the principles of kindness and integrity. To work for a better future for us all.
